byline.contributor: Somini Sengupta contributed reporting from the United Nations.
byline.original: By ROD NORDLAND and SHUAIB ALMOSAWA

abstract: United Nations issues warning that Yemen may collapse as Al Qaeda fighters make large gains there.
lead_paragraph: The militants were said to have completely captured the Yemeni National Army’s 19th Brigade after heavy fighting at its headquarters in the southeast.
